<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#008000">(٧١)</span> بَاب <span style="color:#008000">(الديك الْأَبْيَض صديقي ... الحَدِيث)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قَالَ الْخَطِيب:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" لَا يَصح من هَذَا الحَدِيث وَلَا إِسْنَاده "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>